 S = 1 + 2 + 3 + \cdots + 97 + 98 + 99 
 \begin{align} S &= \ 1 + \ 2 + \ \ 3 + \cdots + 97 + 98 + 99 \\ S &= 99 + 98 + 97 + \cdots + 3 + 2 + 1 \end{align} 
 2S = (1+99) + (2+98) + (3+97) + \cdots + (97+3)+(98+2)+(99+1) 
 2S = \underbrace{100 + 100 + \cdots 100 + 100}_{99\text{ terms}} = 100\cdot99 = 9900 
